Chunk, ChunkInstrument
public class ChunkInstrumentImpl
extends ChunkImpl
implements ChunkInstrument

An implementation of the model object 'Chunk Instrument'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Unshifted Note
  • Fine Tune
  • Gain
  • Low Note
  • High Note
  • Low Velocity
  • High Velocity
